#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/gt70JOD9xsPlpJnuBJAWdOT4yRg.jpg" group-title="|FR| ACTION/AVENTURE" tvg-type="movie" description="An aging ex-boxer gangster working as muscle for a Boston crime boss receives an upsetting diagnosis.  Despite a faltering memory, he attempts to rectify the sins of his past and reconnect with his estranged children. He is determined to leave a positive legacy for his grandson, but the criminal underworld isn’t done with him and won’t loosen their grip willingly." year="2024-10-31" director="Hans Petter Moland, Kit Conners, Colin Flaherty, Daniel Lugo, Frankie Ferrari" actors="Liam Neeson, Ron Perlman, Yolonda Ross, Frankie Shaw, Daniel Diemer",Absolution (2024)
