#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/gtlai95IERRDgRhPCK0WEuwCRP0.jpg" group-title="|FR| ACTION/AVENTURE" tvg-type="movie" description="Four beautiful rivals at an invitation-only martial-arts tournament join forces against a sinister threat. Princess Kasumi is an aristocratic warrior trained by martial-arts masters. Tina Armstrong is a wrestling superstar. Helena Douglas is an athlete with a tragic past. Christie Allen earns her keep as a thief and an assassin-for-hire." year="2006-09-07" director="Corey Yuen Kwai, Deborah Antoniou, Sherrie Liu, Kimiyoshi Adachi, Felice Ning Bee Fei" actors="Jaime Pressly, Holly Valance, Sarah Carter, Devon Aoki, Natassia Malthe",DOA: Dead or Alive (2006)
