#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/8rdB1wkheEMMqcY8qLAKjCMPcnZ.jpg" group-title="|FR| MANGA" tvg-type="movie" description="In a society devastated by the effects of an all-out war between heroes and villains, a mysterious giant fortress suddenly appears, engulfing towns and people one after another. Then, a man reminiscent of All Might, the 'symbol of peace', stands in front of Izuku and his friends..." year="2024-08-02" director="Tensai Okamura, Tensai Okamura, Tetsuya Miyanishi, Tsuyoshi Tobita, Shinnosuke Ito" actors="Daiki Yamashita, Meru Nukumi, Mamoru Miyano, Kenta Miyake, Nobuhiko Okamoto",My Hero Academia: You're Next (2024)
