#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/pdtzEreKvKAlqa2YEBaGwiA45V8.jpg" group-title="|FR| MANGA" tvg-type="movie" description="Ashitaka, a prince of the disappearing Emishi people, is cursed by a demonized boar god and must journey to the west to find a cure. Along the way, he encounters San, a young human woman fighting to protect the forest, and Lady Eboshi, who is trying to destroy it. Ashitaka must find a way to bring balance to this conflict." year="1997-07-12" director="Hayao Miyazaki, Koji Aritomi, Hiroyuki Ito, Masakatsu Ishizone" actors="Youji Matsuda, Yuriko Ishida, Yūko Tanaka, Kaoru Kobayashi, Masahiko Nishimura",Princess Mononoke (1997)
